name: Premium Global Income Split Corp. Preferred Shares
longDescription: World Financial Split Corp is a Canada-based mutual fund corporation. It invests in a portfolio, which includes common equity securities selected from the largest financial services and real estate companies by market capitalization in each Canada, the United States, and the rest of the countries. The company receives maximum revenue from the dividend income.
